{"_id":"8RdLGc65B7G69hdx","name":"VF-1 Power Suit","permission":{"default":0,"qtb8j5Fh7Hu0wRrz":3},"type":"npc","data":{"abilities":{"str":{"value":"23","proficient":0,"mod":6,"prof":0,"saveBonus":0,"checkBonus":0,"save":8,"dc":14},"dex":{"value":"10","proficient":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"saveBonus":0,"checkBonus":0,"save":2,"dc":8},"con":{"value":"10","proficient":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"saveBonus":0,"checkBonus":0,"save":2,"dc":8},"int":{"value":"10","proficient":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"saveBonus":0,"checkBonus":0,"save":2,"dc":8},"wis":{"value":"10","proficient":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"saveBonus":0,"checkBonus":0,"save":2,"dc":8},"cha":{"value":"10","proficient":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"saveBonus":0,"checkBonus":0,"save":2,"dc":8}},"attributes":{"ac":{"value":"17"},"hp":{"value":30,"min":0,"max":30,"temp":0,"tempmax":0,"formula":""},"init":{"value":0,"bonus":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"total":0},"spellcasting":"int","speed":{"value":"30 ft","special":""},"prof":2,"spelldc":8},"details":{"biography":{"value":"<p>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-rules.T77zvGdp7mn1uopU]{Exo-Armor Rules &amp; Descriptions} @Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-rules.wbgddINY6cseqVgE]{Tech Level 3}</p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Originally built as a heavy lift assistant, the VF-1 found popularity later as a muscle augmenter for weapon applications by the defense department. Eventually a new suit, the </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"color: #242021;\">ATH-Q58 Vertical Tank</span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">, was purposebuilt for the role, but the VF-1’s smaller size kept it in regular use, and it remains the more popular model. Depending on its loadout, it can serve as both a ranged weapons platform and a close-combat vehicle.</span></p>\n<table class=\"NormalTable\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 96px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">VF-1 Power Suit </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 47px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">65,000 </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 158px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">15*+Dex modifier (max 2) </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 28px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">— </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 92px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Disadvantage </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 53px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">650 lb. </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 43px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">H </span></td>\n<td style=\"width: 27px;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">3</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Balance</strong>: For the sake of game balance, the VF-1 counts as one legendary item and two rare items.<br></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Bonus</strong>: The VF-1 has a +2 bonus to AC (17 total). </span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Disruption Recovery</strong>: As a reaction to the armor’s shutdown, the VF-1 comes back online. Once you use this feature , you cannot use it again until you finish a long rest.<br></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Firearm Stabilization</strong>: Even though you are Medium-sized, you can wield heavy weapons as if they are two-handed small arms and super heavy weapons as if they are heavy weapons.<br></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Gauntlets</strong>: Unarmed attacks with the armor do base 1d6 damage. If you already inflict 1d6 or more damage with unarmed attacks, increase the damage dice by one step (1d8 &gt; 1d10 &gt; 1d12 &gt; 2d6 &gt; 2d8 &gt; 2d10). The gauntlets also grant a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls.<br></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-rules.br89VG05tCUMDv4m]{Hit Points &amp; Threshold}</strong>: The VF-1 has 30 hit points and a threshold of 5.<br></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Mecha Fists</strong>: The VF-1 has a Strength of 23.<br></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Power</strong>: The VF-1 requires an H-class power cell to operate and it does not function without it. @Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-equipment.JKcEAJ4xm2Us5hYN]{Battry Cell, High}<br></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Resistances</strong>: You have resistance to fire, acid, and cold, as well as slashing and bludgeoning from nonmagical weapons.<br></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Speed</strong>: Your speed is 30 feet.<br></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Weapon Mount</strong>: The VF-1 has a shoulder or arm mounted assembly, which frees up a hand. This mount acts as a hand or a brace for holding or mounting weapons.</span></p>","public":""},"alignment":"","race":"","type":"Mech","environment":"","cr":1,"spellLevel":0,"xp":{"value":200},"source":"UM5 p.90"},"traits":{"size":"med","di":{"value":[],"custom":""},"dr":{"value":["acid","bludgeoning","cold","fire","slashing"],"custom":""},"dv":{"value":[],"custom":""},"ci":{"value":[],"custom":""},"senses":"","languages":{"value":[],"custom":""}},"currency":{"pp":0,"gp":0,"ep":0,"sp":0,"cp":0},"skills":{"acr":{"value":0,"ability":"dex","bonus":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"total":0,"passive":10},"ani":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","bonus":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"total":0,"passive":10},"arc":{"value":0,"ability":"int","bonus":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"total":0,"passive":10},"ath":{"value":0,"ability":"str","bonus":0,"mod":6,"prof":0,"total":6,"passive":16},"dec":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","bonus":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"total":0,"passive":10},"his":{"value":0,"ability":"int","bonus":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"total":0,"passive":10},"ins":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","bonus":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"total":0,"passive":10},"itm":{"value":0,"ability":"cha","bonus":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"total":0,"passive":10},"inv":{"value":0,"ability":"int","bonus":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"total":0,"passive":10},"med":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","bonus":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"total":0,"passive":10},"nat":{"value":0,"ability":"int","bonus":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"total":0,"passive":10},"prc":{"value":0,"ability":"wis","bonus":0,"mod":0,"prof":0,"total":0,"passive":10},"prf":{